    "Compared to vanilla LoRA, we can find that our proposed MoSLoRA captures more details of the subject and better conforms to the given prompt.",
    "Specifically, MoSLoRA learns more details about the given cat, including the color of the hairs around the neck and the shape of the paw.",
    "Meanwhile, the images from MoSLoRA are more consistent with the given prompts, such as the wet (thus clumped) hair and the floating gesture (spread hands).",
    "We also perform human evaluation on the generated images.",
